name: Speedroid Hexasaucer
desc:
Pendulum Effect
You can target 1 of your WIND Synchro Monster that is banished or in your GY; return it to the Extra Deck. You can only use this effect of "Speedroid Hexasaucer" once per turn.

Monster Effect
Both players take any battle damage involving this card. Any battle damage both players take from battles involving this card is halved. If this card is destroyed while in your Pendulum Zone: You can Special Summon 1 face-up “Speedroid” Pendulum Monster from your Extra Deck.
